  lines:
  - speaker: 1
    text: "That\u2019s interesting so it says here 70/30 is 70% for needs and wants
      while 30% is for saving."
  - speaker: 1
    text: "That\u2019s a good amount but I might spend more on wants than needs\u2026"
  - speaker: 1
    text: Hmm.. What's this 50/30/20? 50% Needs, 30% Wants and 20% Savings? I save
      less though but this does look more manageable
